{"tid":1738298,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"兵者詭道也","createTime":"2019-11-19T08:04:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T08:59:35.000Z","uid":30791,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ec6a3b09cdc9118749493e313d96ccb20903de09","tid":1738298,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T08:04:06.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n<strong>兵者，詭道也</strong><br />\n用兵之道在於千變萬化，出其不意<br />\n<strong>能而示之不能，用而示之不用</strong><br />\n隱藏真正的實力或者是讓不欲人知的訊息隱藏不露<br />\n<strong>近而示之遠，遠而示之近</strong><br />\n將主力或即將要發動的攻勢，佯裝到錯誤的距離及位置，令敵人評估失準<br />\n<strong>利而誘之</strong><br />\n用利益引誘貪利之人<br />\n<strong>亂而取之</strong><br />\n製造混亂，然後再乘虛而入<br />\n<strong>實而備之</strong><br />\n以充足的準備，去面對軍隊整齊有實力的對手<br />\n<strong>強而避之</strong><br />\n對強大士氣旺盛的敵人，先避其鋒，待其疲憊，再尋求反擊的機會<br />\n<strong>怒而撓之</strong><br />\n不斷騷擾敵人，令其破綻百出<br />\n<strong>卑而驕之</strong><br />\n以卑微的態度，令自大的對手失去危機感<br />\n<strong>佚而勞之</strong><br />\n以逸待勞，以最佳狀態迎接奔波疲勞的敵人<br />\n<strong>親而離之</strong><br />\n接近敵人的親信，然後進行離間行為，令其內外孤立<br />\n<strong>攻其不備</strong><br />\n攻擊對手無防備，或較薄弱的地方<br />\n<strong>出其不意</strong><br />\n在對手意想不到的地方及情勢下發動攻擊<br />\n<strong>＜孫子兵法 始計篇＞</strong><br />\n</div>"},{"pid":"cfaed9323b70ba9170c5b7c15dbd33b683f6f46b","tid":1738298,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T08:04:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"137ab57949f5317561512c4363a2da8d5ec05131","tid":1738298,"uid":3522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T08:07:21.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"f2f281d6373f6da640f8d9fd3ba127160f54c725","tid":1738298,"uid":12256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T08:08:11.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3b94e75246e45dab59c81a6e1bdaf5cd211e7fe","tid":1738298,"uid":88133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T08:11:12.000Z","msg":"孫子兵法係好野黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔知點解咁多個月都無咩人提過<br />\n凈係9up毛澤東個句鎮壓學生運動沒有好下場有鳩用咩"},{"pid":"045ca7b12ef5eb45f428ce94139dc65f8845f64d","tid":1738298,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3b94e75246e45dab59c81a6e1bdaf5cd211e7fe","tid":1738298,"uid":88133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T08:11:12.000Z","msg":"孫子兵法係好野黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔知點解咁多個月都無咩人提過<br />\n凈係9up毛澤東個句鎮壓學生運動沒有好下場有鳩用咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T08:16:05.000Z","msg":"我幾個月之前已經講緊"},{"pid":"c440c5942937e76109443dc19186a9efc68dd7ed","tid":1738298,"uid":335348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T08:18:57.000Z","msg":"Push<br />\n<br />\n另外，一番肺腑連同深度分析，大家都可以睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1738105/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1738105/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"36db8e96c8b55c69ceb461251f87604e556843f2","tid":1738298,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T09:20:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e97769b8f4f0bab3eebde60c8ffaba19bd7db28","tid":1738298,"uid":173016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T09:27:56.000Z","msg":"推 日L日咁開花，漫無目的唔係辦法，手足們要學下前人智慧<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ff35d06c428a64f384ff4c47a69e29b831c4dc7","tid":1738298,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T11:14:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cadc334e014b50b456a4639ea8623165c0343418","tid":1738298,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T12:50:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75d4233578a095a9ec8e772cbc0a15e7c21edf6a","tid":1738298,"uid":310494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T12:53:26.000Z","msg":"毛澤東十大軍事原則 簡單貼地易明<br />\n<br />\n1.先打分散和孤立之敵，後打集中和強大之敵。<br />\n<br />\n2.先取小城市、中等城市和廣大鄉村，後取大城市。<br />\n<br />\n3.以殲滅敵人有生力量為主要目標，不以保守或奪取城市和地方為主要目標，保守或奪取城市和地方，是殲滅敵人有生力量的結果。<br />\n<br />\n4.集中絕對優勢兵力，四面包圍敵人力求全殲，給敵人殲滅性的打擊。力求避免打那種得不償失的、或得失相當的消耗戰。<br />\n<br />\n5.不打無準備之仗，不打無把握之仗，每戰都應力求有準備，力求在敵我條件對比下有勝利的把握。<br />\n<br />\n6.發揚勇敢戰鬥、不怕犧牲、不怕疲勞和連續作戰的作風。<br />\n<br />\n7.力求在運動中殲滅敵人。同時，注重陣地攻擊戰術，奪取敵人的據點和城市。<br />\n<br />\n8.在攻城問題上，一切敵人守備薄弱的據點和城市，堅決奪取之。一切敵人有中等程度的守備、而環境又許可加以奪取的據點和城市，相機奪取之。一切敵人守備強固的據點和城市，則等候條件成熟時然後奪取之。<br />\n<br />\n9.以俘獲敵人的全部武器和大部人員，補充自己。我軍人力物力的來源，主要在前線。<br />\n<br />\n10.善於利用兩個戰役之間的間隙，休息和整訓部隊。休整的時間，一般地不要過長，盡可能不使敵人獲得喘息的時間。"},{"pid":"05cf23ac664f4d4d692521e9ba34896ec369d812","tid":1738298,"uid":60120,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T13:00:09.000Z","msg":"呢幾個星期絕對係輸心態<br />\n覺得有火魔就乜都做到<br />\n太依賴了"},{"pid":"647869ffe0ba54e5213a3ac06381ca35c08e49e8","tid":1738298,"uid":14087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T13:06:12.000Z","msg":"無遠射程有傷害性 完"},{"pid":"98e8125781c9df58042dba7a92d59a592c92acaf","tid":1738298,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05cf23ac664f4d4d692521e9ba34896ec369d812","tid":1738298,"uid":60120,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T13:00:09.000Z","msg":"呢幾個星期絕對係輸心態<br />\n覺得有火魔就乜都做到<br />\n太依賴了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T13:08:39.000Z","msg":"我認為最大問題係 死守陣地 正面對抗<br />\n但係我地既目的從來唔係守到最後<br />\n而係亂到最後"},{"pid":"14ff90a5e8b4af1871d04ee86d37c353cd120bd4","tid":1738298,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T05:19:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f69434faba1252dbb74c99ed4a0c55ce14814d23","tid":1738298,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T10:14:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af990719a449c3cebed8bcb2f3c82cf05c6dae0f","tid":1738298,"uid":171742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05cf23ac664f4d4d692521e9ba34896ec369d812","tid":1738298,"uid":60120,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T13:00:09.000Z","msg":"呢幾個星期絕對係輸心態<br />\n覺得有火魔就乜都做到<br />\n太依賴了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T10:48:21.000Z","msg":"對家進化咗，黑狗魔法飛彈射程達150米，而且有閃光彈AOE，debuff致盲致聾。<br />\n<br />\n義士火魔法Wall of Fire只有5～10米，只能防不能攻，根本無法正面硬攻。"},{"pid":"c6935c5fb90a72e6da04b4e17245334ae54223ae","tid":1738298,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T08:49:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a1b7b82e951815611cf8402be870bdecf7bd70e","tid":1738298,"uid":51913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T08:52:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9410ea90d718f66f6ab7df0323db06deca6f672f","tid":1738298,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T08:59:35.000Z","msg":"&laquo;墨子&bull;號令&raquo;：「凡守城者以亟傷敵為上，其延日持久以待救之至，明於守者也，不能此，乃能守城。」"}]}